{"tid":1499581,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[824觀塘遊行]睇下智能燈柱又發現少少野","createTime":"2019-08-23T18:26:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T06:01:42.000Z","uid":48912,"like":66,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"54ad71cff10695c9028dec2efb16fe181ba005d9","tid":1499581,"uid":48912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:26:49.000Z","msg":"824觀塘遊行其中一個主題係智能燈柱<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/kt-09_7wFz1_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fkt-09_7wFz1_1200x0.png&h=93ad3c7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我睇返以前de post 同資料<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3068578/org/0a4561cef9db710b2ee65bfb2bb4fdb9.jpg/5Ph-sT3ibUFxvNJKmxoeRnAlaqeR7hqcbALPz2wCz88?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3068578%2Forg%2F0a4561cef9db710b2ee65bfb2bb4fdb9.jpg%2F5Ph-sT3ibUFxvNJKmxoeRnAlaqeR7hqcbALPz2wCz88%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=fc754522&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1264204/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1264204/page/1</a>(簡介下智能燈柱)<br />\n<img src=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20190717/photo/0717-00176-045b1.jpg?t=1566581718465\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190717%2Fphoto%2F0717-00176-045b1.jpg%3Ft%3D1566581718465&h=b5a1a4da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n暫時最多資料係東方條片<br />\n<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20190717/00176_045.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190717%2F00176_045.html&d=iLyAB%2BOE6twWPMF9W2uC6nwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=d7e56c72\" target=\"_blank\">https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20190717/00176_045.html</a><br />\n佢有close up 影過下智能燈柱下面個道門<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0LKO4EW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0LKO4EW.png&h=0a7db020&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n火牛加散熱<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gjcw2rD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGjcw2rD.png&h=afaad146&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Fuse 制<br />\n關左上面無電就可以做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最好有他筆驗下電先但唔建議試<br />\n始終帶電</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G8ckVME.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG8ckVME.png&h=87beaee7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n出線，無咩特別但繼續睇片<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8v9b2rF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8v9b2rF.png&h=7624144d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H6Aq6Tf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH6Aq6Tf.jpg&h=487f5278&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有兩條直飛上去無經 Fuse<br />\n可能唔係電係其他野?<br />\n例如傳送資料／5G同WiFi 的數據線(光纖?)<br />\n如果係光纖，剪左就煩過電線好多好多好多好多<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但唔排除真係電線，有電就仆直</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁點算?我又搵到幅圖<br />\n<img src=\"http://smartcity.cps.com.cn/static/upload/201904/1556586530253698.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsmartcity.cps.com.cn%2Fstatic%2Fupload%2F201904%2F1556586530253698.png&h=2e5c1c6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個似係條片入面打唔開最高個格，個條黃線似光纖?<br />\n但最高個格高過人頭，難以開啟確實<br />\n<br />\n以上係我對智能燈柱的發現<br />\n<br />\n另外搵到條片係質疑高清鏡頭的必要性<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pJA91y0oulU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpJA91y0oulU&d=iLyAB%2BOE6twWPMF9W2uC6nwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=24486ebb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pJA91y0oulU</a><br />\n<br />\n片中提及的新聞<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/2018/10/20181004/20181004_155008_424.html?type=ticker\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.gov.hk%2Fchi%2F2018%2F10%2F20181004%2F20181004_155008_424.html%3Ftype%3Dticker&d=iLyAB%2BOE6twWPMF9W2uC6nwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=a33c8378\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/2018/10/20181004/20181004_155008_424.html?type=ticker</a><br />\n    由一間德國半導體公司在科學園設置的智慧燈柱裝有<span style=\"color: red;\">雷達</span>，能偵測附近車流和人流，協助疏導交通。<br />\n...<br />\n    潘大偉又指，雷達不受天氣和光線影響，較照相機、超聲波或紅外線可靠，<span style=\"color: red;\">也沒有鏡頭，不會構成私隱問題。</span><br />\n<br />\n最後附上智慧燈柱技術多面睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201907/16/P2019071600963.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201907%2F16%2FP2019071600963.htm&d=iLyAB%2BOE6twWPMF9W2uC6nwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=720b8036\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201907/16/P2019071600963.htm</a>"},{"pid":"c5cf85aeeedb93f1fa3de88b831ab22296109665","tid":1499581,"uid":48912,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:28:28.000Z","msg":"本人只係想討論下智能燈柱<br />\n一齊討論下智能燈柱啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c8791f2a90f5db046fbe4b96787b901315b44cd","tid":1499581,"uid":48912,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:29:04.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"83b348cf1b24f951b38e5410559a050c182a7b45","tid":1499581,"uid":286964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:29:08.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<br />\n被控義士們依家點？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1499004\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1499004</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f7c94c2534302bbdf9f2068887d22ce40444b386","tid":1499581,"uid":569,"like":0,"dislike":